{"tid":1889023,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90後夏日行山玩澗group","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T12:24:00.000Z","uid":68142,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5484bf5cd14b495e0a23be5459aa6d54a2d4490b","tid":1889023,"uid":68142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"我地係幾個好鍾意香港山水嘅90後,平時大部份時間都係山上面過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊天氣暖返想誠邀志同道合嘅連登仔女一齊行下山郊遊下,因為香港其實係好靚身為香港人應該主動睇多啲自己屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣再熱啲我地會玩下澗或者綑岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我地豐檢由人有新手路線都有帶小小挑戰性嘅嘅線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲有興趣嘅朋友可以填咗下面google form入whatsapp group傾下山經,或者你有癮都可以你開團我地無任歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位連登仔快啲入group行山抗疫啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfjpZT2suGQt8aIGefjJ4I7sCTd_-onbDHpm7VvMEjxWlpZDQ/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfjpZT2suGQt8aIGefjJ4I7sCTd_-onbDHpm7VvMEjxWlpZDQ%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=fc98bb3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfjpZT2suGQt8aIGefjJ4I7sCTd_-onbDHpm7VvMEjxWlpZDQ/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kd2rwdJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkd2rwdJ.jpg&h=ab0a6311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBMDnkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBMDnkp.jpg&h=44014a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHZadr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHZ